er is\",\"id\":\"Nomor Mandiri Virtual Account Anda adalah\"},\"INPUT NOKK NUMBER\":{\"en\":\"Input NOKK Number\",\"id\":\"Masukan Nomor NOKK\"},\"FOOTER.CALL.DESC\":{\"en\":\"\",\"id\":\"\"},\"INVOICE\":{\"en\":\"Invoice\",\"id\":\"Faktur  \"},\"BACK TO HOME\":{\"en\":\"Back To Home\",\"id\":\"Kembali ke Beranda\"},\"OTPSENTTOYOURMOBILENUMBER\":{\"en\":\"OTP Sent to your Mobile number\",\"id\":\"OTP Dikirim ke nomor Ponsel Anda\"},\"CREATEUPDATEPASSWORDPAGE.DIGITLIMIT\":{\"en\":\"At least 1 digit\",\"id\":\"minimal 1 angka\"},\"COMMON.LASTLOGIN\":{\"en\":\"Last Login\",\"id\":\"Login terakhir\"},\"OC.CHKCOVERAGE\":{\"en\":\"Check Coverage\",\"id\":\"Cek Area Jangkauan\"},\"STARTING FROM\":{\"en\":\"Starting from\",\"id\":\"Mulai dari\"},\"SUBSCRIPTIONPAGE.INSTALLATIONDETAILS.SUBSCRIBEDTITLE\":{\"en\":\"Thank you for choosing the Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison indosat HiFi service\",\"id\":\"Terima kasih telah memilih layanan Indosat HiFi dari Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison\"},\"WEWILLNOTIFYYOUIFTHERESANISSUEFROMDATAYOUVEUPLOADED\":{\"en\":\"We will notify you if there’s an issue from data you’ve uploaded\",\"id\":\"Kami akan menginformasikan jika data yang kamu unggah bermasalah.\"},\"THENEWPLANWILLSTARTEFFECTIVELYFROM1STOFNEXTMONTH\":{\"en\":\"The new plan will start effectively from 1st of next month\",\"id\":\"Rencana baru akan mulai efektif mulai tanggal 1 bulan depan\"},\"TERMINATION.MEASSAGE_ONE\":{\"en\":\"please note that our backend team will analyze and\",\"id\":\"harap dicatat bahwa tim backend kami akan menganalisis dan\"},\"IPTVSTBTYPE\":{\"en\":\"IPTV STB Type\",\"id\":\"Jenis IPTV STB\"},\"HIFIAIR.HIFIAIRLIST.ITEM4.ICON\":{\"en\":\"/images/img/hifiair/ic-myhifi05.svg\",\"id\":\"/images/img/hifiair/ic-myhifi05.svg\"},\"NEW_ALERT_LABEL_IDREGISTRATION1\":{\"en\":\"Cek status NIK kamu\",\"id\":\"Cek status NIK kamu\"},\"HOMEPAGE.ABOUTUSPRODUCTSECTION.DESCRIPTION2\":{\"en\":\"\",\"id\":\"\"},\"HIFIAIR.BANNERS.WEBBANNERID\":{\"en\":\"40\",\"id\":\"40\"},\"HOMEPAGE.ABOUTUSPRODUCTSECTION.DESCRIPTION1\":{\"en\":\"\",\"id\":\"\"},\"TERMSANDCONDITIONSOFADVANCEPAYMENT\":{\"en\":\"Terms and Conditions of Advance Payment Program with Deposit Model:\",\"id\":\"Syarat dan Ketentuan Program Pembayaran Advance Payment dengan Model Deposito:\"},\"ENTERCUSTOMERIDMOBILENUMBEREMAILID\":{\"en\":\"Enter Customer ID /Billing ID / Mobile Number /Email ID\",\"id\":\"Masukkan ID Pelanggan ID Penagihan /Nomor Ponsel /ID Email\"},\"UNLMT_SERACH_LOCATION_DATA_AV_TTL\":{\"en\":\"Yeay! HiFi Air Unlimited is available in your area. Get it from the nearest outlet or visit\",\"id\":\"Yeay! HiFi Air Unlimited tersedia di daerah kamu. Dapatkan layanan ini di outlet terdekat atau kunjungi\"},\"VASENTERTAINMENTPACK\":{\"en\":\"VAS - Entertainment Pack\",\"id\":\"VAS - Paket Hiburan\"},\"PAY NOW\":{\"en\":\"Pay Now\",\"id\":\"Bayar\"},\"OTHERSERVICES\":{\"en\":\"Other Services\",\"id\":\"Layanan lainnya\"},\"ACCOUNT TERMINATION\":{\"en\":\"Account Termination\",\"id\":\"Pengakhiran Akun\"},\"PROCEED\":{\"en\":\"-Proceed\",\"id\":\"-Lanjutkan\"},\"UPLOADLIMITSUPPORTEDFILESIZE\":{\"en\":\"Upload limit supported until 5MB\",\"id\":\"Batas unggahan didukung hingga 5MB\"},\"COMMON.MONTH\":{\"en\":\"Month\",\"id\":\"Month\"},\"COMMON.DIFFHOME\":{\"en\":\"Different Home\",\"id\":\"Different Home\"},\"SUCCESSFULLYSUBMITTEDTHECASE\":{\"en\":\"Successfully submitted the case\",\"id\":\"Berhasil menyerahkan kasus tersebut\"},\"SUBSCRIPTIONPAGE.SUBSCRIPTIONS.SUBSCRIPTIONTYPE\":{\"en\":\"Your Subscription Type\",\"id\":\"Tipe berlangganan\"},\"CONFIRMNEWPASSWORD\":{\"en\":\"Confirm New Password\",\"id\":\"Konfirmasi Password Baru\"},\"ENTERTAINMENT\":{\"en\":\"Entertainment\",\"id\":\"Hiburan\"},\"SUBSCRIPTIONPAGE.INSTALL_DATE\":{\"en\":\"Installation Date\",\"id\":\"Tanggal pemasangan\"},\"ALLABOUTYOURPLANANDALLOWYOUTOMANAGEYOUROWNACCOUNT\":{\"en\":\"All about your plan and allow you to manage your account on your own\",\"id\":\"Ringkasan tentang paket berlangganan dan pengelolaan akun kamu\"},\"FAILED TO INITIATE PAYMENT\":{\"en\":\"Failed to initiate payment\",\"id\":\"Failed to initiate payment\"},\"CASENUMBER\":{\"en\":\"Case Number\",\"id\":\"Nomor kasus\"},\"COMMON.OTHERSADDRESSDET\":{\"en\":\"e.g. Block/Unit No., Landmarks\",\"id\":\"contoh: Blok/Unit No. Patokan\"},\"SUSPENTION.SUSPENDED\":{\"en\":\"account suspended\",\"id\":\"Akun Ditangguhkan\"},\"NIK NUMBER\":{\"en\":\"NIK Number\",\"id\":\"Nomor NIK\"},\"COMMON.RELOCATIONTYPE\":{\"en\":\"Relocation Type\",\"id\":\"Relocation Type\"},\"YOUROTPHASBEENVERIFIEDANDYOURORDERHASBEENSENTFORVERIFICATION\":{\"en\":\"Your OTP has been verified and your order has been sent for verification.\",\"id\":\"OTP telah terverifikasi dan pesanan kamu telah dikirim untuk proses verifikasi\"},\"STBDETAILS\":{\"en\":\"STB Details\",\"id\":\"Detail STB\"},\"PLEASETAKEAPPROPRIATEACTIONTOPROCEED\":{\"en\":\"Please take appropriate action to proceed\"},\"OTHERBILLINGACCOUNTS\":{\"en\":\"Other Account Number\",\"id\":\"Nomor akun lain\"},\"HOMEPAGE.SPECIALATTRACTIONSECTION.CARD2.DESCRIPTION\":{\"en\":\"1. High speed internet that won\\u0027t be disturbed even during peak hours.\\n2. Faster upload and download speeds\\n3. Use of multiple gadgets at the same time without interruption.\",\"id\":\"1. Internet berkecepatan tinggi yang tidak akan terganggu walaupun di jam-jam sibuk.\\n2. Download dan upload file lebih cepat\\n3. Penggunaan banyak gadget pada saat yang bersamaan tanpa gangguan.\"},\"ACCOUNTOREMAILID\":{\"en\":\"Account ID\",\"id\":\"ID Akun\"},\"COMMON.CONFIRMATION\":{\"en\":\"Confirmation\",\"id\":\"Konfirmasi\"},\"INPUTCORRESPONDINGEMAILADDRESS\":{\"en\":\"Input Corresponding Email Address\",\"id\":\"Masukan email lainnya\"},\"BUYERISOBLIGATEDTOFINISH\":{\"en\":\"Buyer is obligated to finish the Card’s purchase and payment by following the procedure that is defined by Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison\",\"id\":\"Pembeli wajib menyelesaikan pembelian dan pembayaran dengan Kartu dengan mengikuti prosedur yang ditentukan oleh Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison\"},\"NEWSPAGE.ARTICLE1.DESCRIPTION\":{\"en\":\"Great news for us Indonesian netizens! As part of the commitment to provide a highly reliable home internet service for all kinds of digital activities, Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison has launched its newest Indosat HiFi service on Friday, September 9, 2022, in Indosat Ooredoo KPPTI auditorium.\\nHosted by Inga Aulina, the grand launching event of Indosat HiFi was held with the theme `The Future of #TrulyReliable Fiber Internet Service`. Attended by Vikram Sinha, President Director \\u0026 CEO of Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison, and Johnny G. Plate, the Minister of Communication and Information Technology, the two influential figures in digitizing Indonesia, symbolically launched Indosat HiFi at the opening event.\\nWith the huge potential that Indonesia\\u0027s digital economic growth possesses, the minister also declares his appreciation toward Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison for answering the rapidly increasing need for internet connection through Indosat HiFi as a fiber-to-home internet connection.\\nMr. Chaitanya Priya, as FTTH Lead Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison, also attended the event to explain the main audience segment and the various roles of Indosat HiFi to maximize their digital experience. During the event, he emphasized the 4 points that differentiate Indosat HiFi from other internet services: a better subscription experience, attractive offers for new customers, the presence of O2O or online-to-offline, as well as high sensitivity to the public market.\\nThe grand launching event also held a Q\\u0026A session hosted by Steve Saerang, SVP-Head of Corporate Communications Indosat Ooredoo, to talk about how Indosat HiFi emerges as a #TrulyReliable home internet service for all kinds of digital activities at home. With 100% optical fibers and digital-based service, Indosat HiFi is expected to provide a more accessible consumer experience. As for Indosat Hifi�s coverage has now reached Jabodetabek, Yogyakarta, and Surabaya, Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison will keep the expansion going.\\nThe discussion with Chaitanya Priya was accompanied by Dedy Irvan, also known as Jagat Review, to demonstrate Indosat HiFi 100 Mbps package live on air. He proved its consistency and symmetric speed quality (1:1) for download and upload activities. Not only that, Indosat HiFi also committed to providing 3 internet service packages with competitive prices starting from only IDR 245,000/month.\",\"id\":\"Kabar baik untuk para warga dan netizen Indonesia! Berkomitmen untuk menciptakan layanan internet rumah yang selalu bisa diandalkan untuk segala aktivitas digital, Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison telah meluncurkan layanan Indosat HiFi pada hari Jumat, 9 September 2022 di auditorium Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison KPPTI. \\nDipandu oleh host Inga Aulina, acara grand launching Indosat HiFi mengusung tema “Layanan Internet Fiber Masa Depan yang #NyataAndalnya”. Dihadiri oleh Bapak Vikram Sinha selaku, President Director \\u0026 CEO Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison dan Johnny G. Plate selaku Menteri Komunikasi dan Informatika Republik Indonesia, kedua tokoh penting dalam digitalisasi Indonesia ini meresmikan Indosat HiFi secara simbolis saat pembukaan acara.\\nDidasari oleh besarnya potensi perkembangan ekonomi digital di Indonesia, menteri KOMINFO RI juga tidak lupa menyatakan apresiasinya kepada Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison karena telah menjawab kebutuhan koneksi internet yang kian meningkat dengan Indosat HiFi sebagai layanan internet rumah berbasis teknologi fiber-to-home. \\nTidak hanya itu, Bapak Chaitanya Priya selaku FTTH Lead Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison juga hadir untuk memaparkan lebih jauh mengenai segmen audiens utama dan berbagai peran Indosat HiFi untuk bisa memaksimalkan pengalaman digital mereka. Saat acara berlangsung, beliau juga menekankan 4 poin pembeda Indosat HiFi dengan layanan internet lainnya yaitu pengalaman berlangganan yang lebih baik, penawaran menarik bagi pelanggan baru, keberadaan O2O atau online-to-offline, juga sensitivitas tinggi terhadap pasar masyarakat.\\nAcara grand launching ini juga mengadakan sesi tanya jawab yang dipandu oleh Steve Saerang selaku SVP-Head of Corporate Communications Indosat Ooredoo Hutchison untuk membahas bagaimana Indosat HiFi hadir sebagai layanan internet rumah yang #NyataAndalnya untuk segala aktivitas digital di rumah. Dengan teknologi 100% serat optik dan layanan berbasis digital, Indosat HiFi diharapkan dapat mempermudah pengalaman berlangganan konsumen. Coverage Indosat HiFi sekarang mencakup Jabodetabek, Yogyakarta, dan Surabaya dibarengi dengan upaya indosat Ooredoo Hutchison untuk terus melakukan ekspansi yang lebih luas.\\nPerbincangan bersama Bapak Chaitanya Priya juga diramaikan oleh Dedy Irvan atau yang dikenal sebagai Jagat Review untuk mendemonstrasikan paket layanan Internet Indosat HiFi 100 Mbps secara live. Ia membuktikan konsistensi dan kualitas kecepatan koneksi Indosat HiFi yang simetris (1:1) untuk aktivitas download dan upload. Tidak hanya itu, Indosat HiFi juga berkomitmen untuk menyediakan 3 paket layanan internet rumah dengan harga bersaing, dimulai dari Rp.245.000,-/bulan saja.\"},\"CSAT_FEEDBACK_LABLE_LIKE\":{\"en\":\"What you like?\",\"id\":\"Alasan\"},\"FORGOTPASSWORD\":{\"en\":\"Forgot Password ?\",\"id\":\"Lupa Password ?\"},\"PAYIMMEDIATELY\":{\"en\":\"Pay Immediately\"},\"SUBSCRIPTIONPAGE.SUBSCRIPTIONSUMMARYSTNC\":{\"en\":\"266\",\"id\":\"266\"},\"ENTERANEWPASSWORD\":{\"en\":\"Enter a new password\",\"id\":\"Masukan kata sandi yang baru\"},\"MORE INFORMATION\":{\"en\":\"More Info\",\"id\":\"Informasi Lebih Lanjut\"},\"HIFIAIR.INTROSECTION.ITEMCOUNT\":{\"en\":\"3\",\"id\":\"3\"},\"CHOOSEYOURPREFERREDFTTHINTERNETPACKAGE\":{\"en\":\"Choose your preferred FTTH internet package\",\"id\":\"Pilih paket internet FTTH pilihan Anda\"},\"ONT_GETTING_MODEM_STATUS\":{\"en\":\"Getting Modem Status\",\"id\":\"Memuat status modem\"},\"PROFILE.ORDERHISTORYDESC\":{\"en\":\