whole information.\",\"id\":\"Pembeli bertanggung jawab untuk membaca, memahami, dan menyetujui seluruh informasi.\"},\"PAYNOW\":{\"en\":\"Pay Now\"},\"LIONSGATE.ENABLELGP\":{\"en\":\"A\",\"id\":\"A\"},\"ONT_CHECK_INTERNET_STATUS\":{\"en\":\"Check Internet Status\",\"id\":\"Cek Status Internet\"},\"PLN METER NUMBER\":{\"en\":\"PLN Meter Number\",\"id\":\"Nomor Meter PLN\"},\"KTPPERSONAL.VERIFIED\":{\"en\":\"Your KTP \\u0026 Personal Details Verified\",\"id\":\"KTP \\u0026 Data Pribadi Anda Terverifikasi\"},\"FREE PACK!!!\":{\"en\":\"Free Pack!!!\",\"id\":\"Free Pack!!!\"},\"COMMON.DATE\":{\"en\":\"Date\",\"id\":\"Tanggal\"},\"PAGES.ONLYFORMEDIAINQUIRIES\":{\"en\":\"Only for media inquiries\",\"id\":\"Hanya untuk pertanyaan media\"},\"REGISTEREDTNCTEXT\":{\"en\":\"I agree to receive OTPs and updates on WhatsApp to this mobile number\",\"id\":\"Saya bersedia menerima OTP dan informasi terbaru melalui WhatsApp di nomor ini.\"},\"SUSPENSION.SUSPENDED.TITLE\":{\"en\":\"suspension request not allowed\",\"id\":\"suspension request not allowed\"},\"DB.SENDOTP\":{\"en\":\"Send OTP\",\"id\":\"Send OTP\"},\"HIFIAIRREG.PROCEED\":{\"en\":\"Proceed\",\"id\":\"Lanjutkan\"},\"NEXT24\":{\"en\":\"next 24hrs.\",\"id\":\"24 jam berikutnya.\"},\"YOUR HIFI AIR CARD REGISTRATION IS NOT SUCCESSFUL\":{\"en\":\"Your HiFi Air Card Registration is NOT SUCCESSFUL\",\"id\":\"Registrasi Kartu HiFi Air kamu TIDAK  BERHASIL\"},\"ONT_TRY_AGAIN\":{\"en\":\"Try Restarting Again\",\"id\":\"Coba Restart Ulang\"},\"SCHEDULEINSTALLATION\":{\"en\":\"Scheduled Installation\",\"id\":\"Instalasi terjadwal\"},\"SUBSCRIPTIONPAGE.PERSONALDATA.SUPPORTTEXT\":{\"en\":\"All we need is your address to get started\",\"id\":\"Yang kami butuhkan hanyalah alamat Anda untuk memulai\"},\"ONT_NO_CONNECTED_DEVICES_FOUND\":{\"en\":\"No connected devices found\",\"id\":\"Tidak ada perangkat yang terhubung\"},\"SUSPENTIONTAB.NOTIFICATION\":{\"en\":\"Suspension can only be done maximum 3 times a year\",\"id\":\"Penangguhan akun hanya bisa dilakukan maksimal 3 kali dalam setahun\"},\"LOGINPAGE.ROUTEURL\":{\"en\":\"/login\",\"id\":\"/login\"},\"OTP CODE SENT\":{\"en\":\"OTP Code was sent to your number\",\"id\":\"Kode OTP telah dikirimkan\"},\"FREEPACK\":{\"en\":\"Free Pack\",\"id\":\"Paket Gratis\"},\"PAGES.INSTALLATIONADDRESS\":{\"en\":\"MNCINSTALLATIONADDRESS\",\"id\":\"MNCINSTALLATIONADDRESS\"},\"CANCELDESC\":{\"en\":\"Changes will not be saved and you will need to create the case from the beginning.\",\"id\":\"Perubahan tidak akan disimpan dan Anda harus membuat kasus dari awal.\"},\"REQUESTRECEIVED\":{\"en\":\"Request received\"},\"OC.LOCNOTFOUND\":{\"en\":\"Didn’t find your location?\",\"id\":\"Belum menemukan lokasimu?\"},\"DATACOLLECTION.APIURL\":{\"en\":\"/pages/datacollection\",\"id\":\"/pages/datacollection\"},\"LOCATIONS.NODATAFOUND\":{\"en\":\"Sorry, Indosat HiFi service is not available in this location.\",\"id\":\"Maaf, layanan Indosat HiFi belum tersedia di lokasi ini.\"},\"CPPADDSUCMSG\":{\"en\":\"Upgrade request processed successfully\",\"id\":\"Upgrade request processed successfully\"},\"ENJOY THE NEW EXPERIENCE\":{\"en\":\"Enjoy the new experience of internet browsing with family and friends at home, only with HiFI Air.\",\"id\":\"Nikmati internet dengan pengalaman yang baru dengan HiFi Air bersama keluarga atau teman dirumah.\"},\"SAMEHOME\":{\"en\":\"Same Home\",\"id\":\"Sama Rumah\"},\"COMMON.IMMEDIATELY\":{\"en\":\"Immediately\",\"id\":\"Segera\"},\"STATUS\":{\"en\":\"Status\",\"id\":\"Status\"},\"COMMON.PLEASEWAIT\":{\"en\":\"Please wait\",\"id\":\"Mohon tunggu\"},\"CHATBOT\":{\"en\":\"Chatbot\",\"id\":\"bot obrolan\"},\"DB.PAYMYBILL\":{\"en\":\"Pay My Bill\",\"id\":\"Pay My Bill\"},\"PROFILE.UNPAID\":{\"en\":\"Unpaid\",\"id\":\"Unpaid\"},\"OTHERTHANNEWTICKETDESC\":{\"en\":\"Please check our team’s response below. If you have more questions, please reply to our team within the available time limit or resolve this case to close it.\",\"id\":\"Silakan periksa tanggapa