"Alamat layanan\"},\"SUSPENTION.SUSPENDED.PROGRESS.MESSAGE\":{\"en\":\"Your suspension is already in progress\",\"id\":\"Permintaan penangguhan akun sedang dalam proses\"},\"COMMON.UNABLE_SCHEDULE_APPOINTMENT\":{\"en\":\"unable to schedule appointment\",\"id\":\"Tidak dapat menjadwalkan kunjungan\"},\"VOICEBOT\":{\"en\":\"Voice bot\",\"id\":\"Voice bot\"},\"ONLYINDONESIANNUMBER\":{\"en\":\"Only Indonesian number\",\"id\":\"Hanya nomor Indonesia\"},\"BILLISREADY\":{\"en\":\"@month bill is Ready\",\"id\":\"Tagihan @month telah tersedia\"},\"CPPIMMEDIATELYPAYMENT\":{\"en\":\"CPP immediately payment\",\"id\":\"CPP segera pembayaran\"},\"IM3 NETWORK COVERAGE\":{\"en\":\"IM3 Network Coverage is Expanding and More Stable\",\"id\":\"Jangkauan Sinyal IM3 Semakin Luas dan Stabil\"},\"FREE\":{\"en\":\"Free\",\"id\":\"Gratis\"},\"INBOX\":{\"en\":\"Inbox\",\"id\":\"Inbox\"},\"DELETE\":{\"en\":\"Delete\",\"id\":\"Menghapus\"},\"PLEASECALLCUSTOMERCAREFORDOWNGRADEOFYOURACCOUNT\":{\"en\":\"Please call customer care for Downgrade of your account\"},\"ALTERNATIVE_REG_OTP_SDESC\":{\"en\":\"Your alternate number is successfully registered.\",\"id\":\"Nomor alternatif kamu berhasil didaftarkan.\"},\"DESCRIPTION\":{\"en\":\"description\",\"id\":\"Deskripsi\"},\"RESENDCODE\":{\"en\":\"Resend Code\"},\"SELECT OTP DELIVERY METHOD\":{\"en\":\"Select OTP Delivery Method\",\"id\":\"Pilih Metode Pengiriman OTP\"},\"ONLINEPAYMENT.PAY.SUMMARY\":{\"en\":\"Summary\",\"id\":\"ringkasan\"},\"LOCATIONPAGE.PROFILE.AREYOUWANTTORELOCATE\":{\"en\":\"Are you want to relocate to this address?\",\"id\":\"Anda ingin mengubah alamat rumah?\"},\"LIONSGATE.BANNERID_WEB\":{\"en\":\"33\",\"id\":\"33\"},\"CHOOSE ANOTHER PACKAGE\":{\"en\":\"Choose Another Package\",\"id\":\"Pilih Paket Lain\"},\"DIGIT ICCID\":{\"en\":\"Last Digits ICCID\",\"id\":\"Digit terakhir ICCID\"},\"CORRECTSAMPLE\":{\"en\":\"Correct sample\",\"id\":\"Contoh Benar\"},\"UPLOADDOMICILELETTER\":{\"en\":\"Upload Domicile Letter\",\"id\":\"Upload surat domisili\"},\"ENTERMOBILENUMBER\":{\"en\":\"Enter Mobile Number\",\"id\":\"Masukkan Nomor Ponsel\"},\"HOMEPAGE.SPEEDRECOMMENDATIONSECTION.DESCRIPTION\":{\"en\":\"Internet speed is the speed of data transfer when using the internet network which is measured in bps (bits per second).\\nThe point is the number of bits of data that are transferred from one computer to another in every second. Internet access speed is divided into two types, namely downstream and upstream.\\nIndosat HiFi offers internet services with Fiber Optic network technology that produces a stable signal and without usage restrictions, without quotas. Also speed without limitation (throttling).\",\"id\":\"Kecepatan internet adalah kecepatan transfer data saat menggunakan jaringan internet yang diukur dalam bps (bit per detik).\\nIntinya adalah jumlah bit data yang ditransfer dari satu komputer ke komputer lain dalam setiap detik. Kecepatan akses internet dibagi menjadi dua jenis, yaitu downstream dan upstream.\\nIndosat HiFi menawarkan layanan internet dengan teknologi jaringan Fiber Optic yang menghasilkan sinyal stabil dan tanpa batasan penggunaan, tanpa kuota dan juga kecepatan tanpa batasan (throttling).\"},\"YOURPROFILESUCCESSFULLYUPDATED\":{\"en\":\"Your profile successfully updated.\",\"id\":\"Profil kamu sudah diperbarui\"},\"SUSPENDEDPAGE.PAYMENT.ITEMKEY_ID\":{\"en\":\"payment_channels_data_id_\",\"id\":\"payment_channels_data_id_\"},\"HIFIAIR_ACCOUNT_NUMBERVALIDATION\":{\"en\":\"The number you provided can’t be used. Please use another active WhatsApp number.\",\"id\":\"Nomor ini belum dapat digunakan. Mohon masukkan nomor WhatsApp lain yang aktif.\"},\"OTHERMENU\":{\"en\":\"Other Menu\",\"id\":\"Menu Lain\"},\"PROFILE.PROFILEINFODESC\":{\"en\":\"Below is the profile information. Please updated the Info\",\"id\":\"Below is the profile information. Please updated the Info\"},\"RELOCATION_INFO_DESC\":{\"en\":\"If you want to relocate your Indosat HiFi service, please contact Indosat HiFi Customer Care at 021 - 3000 1515.\",\"id\":\"Jika Anda ingin relokasi layanan Indosat HiFi Anda, silakan hubungi Indosat HiFi Customer Care di 021 - 3000 1515.\"},\"IDNUMBER\":{\"en\":\"ID Number\",\"id\":\"Nomor ID\"},\"MA.STREETADDRESS\":{\"en\":\"Street Address\",\"id\":\"Alamat\"},\"OPEN\":{\"en\":\"Open\",\"id\":\"Membuka\"},\"COMMON.INSTALLATIONAMOUNT\":{\"en\":\"Installation Amount\",\"id\":\"Instalasi tagihan\"},\"PAGES.MULTIACCOUNTCAMPAIGNS\":{\"en\":\"Campaigns\",\"id\":\"Campaigns\"},\"IM3_REG_FAILED_FROM_CRS\":{\"en\":\"MSISDN registration failed for HiFi Air service, please try again later.\",\"id\":\"Pendaftaran MSISDN untuk layanan HiFi Air gagal, silakan coba lagi nanti.\"},\"COMMON.ENTERMOTHERMAIDEN\":{\"en\":\"Input your Mother’s Maiden Name\",\"id\":\"Masukan Nama Ibu Kandung\"},\"OFFERENDSBY\":{\"en\":\"Offer Ends by\",\"id\":\"Penawaran Berakhir\"},\"DATEOFBIRTH\":{\"en\":\"Date of Birth\",\"id\":\"Tanggal lahir\"},\"ONLINEPAYMENT.BILLING.PAYMENTTEXT\":{\"en\":\"Payment in progress\",\"id\":\"Pembayaran sedang berlangsung\"},\"CHANGEPACKAGE\":{\"en\":\"Change Package\",\"id\":\"Ganti Paket\"},\"MNCRELOCATION.URL\":{\"en\":\"/newrelocation\",\"id\":\"/newrelocation\"},\"LOGOUTTITLE\":{\"id\":\"Apakah Anda yakin ingin keluar akun?\"},\"HIFIAIR.BANNERS.MOBBANNERID\":{\"en\":\"42\",\"id\":\"42\"},\"PAYMENTQRCODEDOWNLOADED\":{\"en\":\"PaymentQRCode Downloaded\"},\"NOTESDETAILS\":{\"id\":\"Pastikan dokumen yang Anda unggah valid, jelas dan tidak buram Gunakan format JPEG atau PNG dengan ukuran file maksimum 4MB Kami akan infokan kepada Anda untuk mengonfirmasi jika ada masalah dari data yang Anda unggah\"},\"SUSPENTION.PENDING.AMOUNT.MESSAGE_ONE\":{\"en\":\"Pay to proceed.\",\"id\":\"Lakukan pembayaran untuk proses selanjutnya.\"},\"COMMON.CONTINUE\":{\"en\":\"Continue\",\"id\":\"Melanjutkan\"},\"PAGES.MNCMULTIACCOUNTCHECKLOCATION\":{\"en\":\"Check Location\",\"id\":\"Check Location\"},\"ALTERNATIVE_REG_OTP_FDESC\":{\"en\":\"We’re currently unable t